    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To assess the long-term effects of early therapeutic intervention, i.e. within two years
      following a first clinical demyelinating event suggestive of MS.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
